{"tid":867551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】巴打，遇見異物，求救。","createTime":"2018-10-18T18:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T04:01:51.000Z","uid":29985,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"03f091e556e26b95140a5166200c7102cfd9d2bf","tid":867551,"uid":29985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:16:15.000Z","msg":"先說背景。<br />\n因為大廈維修工程，所以今日師傅上黎，借屋企窗口出去<span style=\"color: red;\">搭棚</span>。<br />\n<br />\n頭先突然彈出一隻昆蟲，我被嚇到。懷疑依附竹棚上，進入家中。<br />\n想知隻野有無危險，深怕只見一隻郤還有更多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjDGW2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjDGW2R.jpg&h=a5314598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MLx3HT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MLx3HT.jpg&h=ecf5d226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhWdN9z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhWdN9z.jpg&h=6092a0ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jgxgLWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjgxgLWg.jpg&h=6be62bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eENks9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeENks9D.jpg&h=65fe86b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irn1cBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Firn1cBm.jpg&h=0440072c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#捉住之後怕其生猛，唯有整死以求安心，某些圖片只有單腳，但搖極都搖唔死。<br />\n僅憑上述資訊，我不知如何從google獲得昆蟲資料。<br />\ngoogle及wiki無法提供幫助下，我轉向連登尋求幫助。<br />\n望智者幫助小弟。"},{"pid":"810ea497b9426417ac842058f457ef6964998395","tid":867551,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1fjGVp0M80tSs9xLFj/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1fjGVp0M80tSs9xLFj%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b9f671f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"